text: Ani dona samudra samana nahita. Ha goda ahe, tahana bhagavito, pyayala cangala ani to dusara kharata ahe, kadu. Tumhi ya doghampasuna taje mansa khata ani te dagine kadhata, jyanna tumhi angavara ghalata ani tumhi pahata ki mothamothya nava, panyala chedanarya, tya samudrata ahe, yasathi ki tumhi tyacya krpeca sodha ghyava ani yasathi ki tumhi tyace abhara manaveta
